   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <pb facs="#facs_1" n="1" xml:id="img_0001"/>
            <ab facs="#facs_1_r">
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l" n="N001"/>1905/6=Fauvism - <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1343">Monet</rs>, <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1984">V. Gogh</rs>, <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__658">Gauguin</rs>, <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1368">Munch</rs>, <rs type="person">Cusa</rs>
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1" n="N002"/>Colour in late {exp} <Impressionism>impressionism</Impressionism> (<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1343">Monet</rs>) and<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1404"> Nolde</rs>. Ecstasy under refinement
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_2" n="N003"/><Myth>Mythical</Myth> depth of nature. Then the mythical material itself
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_3" n="N004"/>Ecstasy against individualisation. Colour and vision
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_4" n="N005"/><rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__4032">Maria Agyptiaca </rs>(whore and saint)
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_5" n="N006"/>Art of the Primitives as means
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_6" n="N007"/>[<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__4033">Paula Modersohn</rs> - Worpswede]
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_7" n="N008"/>[<rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__4034">Christian Rohlfs</rs>] [Church-Window-similarity]
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_8" n="N009"/><rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__4035">Kirchner</rs>, <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__836">Heckel</rs>, <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__1726">Schmidt-Rottluf</rs>: The "Bridge" / African influence
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_9" n="N010"/>Graphic tendency + bright colour. Contour. Threedimensional by planes
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_10" n="N011"/>Restlessness / Red and yellow / nothing beautifying
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_11" n="N012"/><rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__836">Heckel</rs>: Splitting up of surface. / Fight between picture form
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_12" n="N013"/>and expression. Hieroglyphs of eroticism. Hallucinatory
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_13" n="N014"/>Anti-reproductive picture Encounter
            </ab>
            <pb facs="#facs_2" n="2" xml:id="img_0002"/>
            <ab facs="#facs_2_r">
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l" n="N001"/><rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__4036">Barlach</rs>, power of the <Myth>mythical</Myth>, a world of pilgrims
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_1" n="N002"/>created by himself (Southern Russia)
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_2" n="N003"/>round {pi} blocks. Longing for miracles, begging. Archaism
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_3" n="N004"/>The blue Rider and <rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__4037">Pechstein</rs>. (conventional and successful)
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_4" n="N005"/><rs type="person" key=", tillich_person_id__172">Beckmann</rs>. Heroic dreams, big format. Experience of
               <lb facs="#facs_2_l_5" n="N006"/>war. Considering wild presence
            </ab>
         </div>
      </body>
